data.description: Stunningly renovated ranch home featuring a finished basement, boasting new flooring and lighting fixtures throughout. Enjoy a brand new kitchen adorned with 42 inch soft close cabinets, quartz counters and new backsplash complemented by renovated bathrooms for a touch of luxury. The cozy ambiance is enhanced with the shiplap detailing above the fireplace, while the sleek subway tile shower adds a modern flair. Experience comfort and style in every corner of this meticulously updated property with a 4 car tandem garage and fenced yard.
